My key takeaways:
▶️ I’m in it not of it (social media)

▶️ It’s hard to hate up close! 

▶️ Turn those despites into triumphs.

▶️ There are diamonds all over this earth.

▶️ Protect your light. 

▶️ Learn which friends to let in and friends to let out.

Mom & I played tourists in NYC today. We he checked out the @louisvuitton 200 Trunks exhibit in the old Barney’s building.

My word for 2023 is perseverance!

The definition is a continued effort to do or achieve something despite difficulties, failure, or opposition : the action or condition or an instance of persevering.

The reason I selected this word is after experiencing a difficult 2022 which included the loss of my stepfather and family matriarch, leaving a role with a long standing client, and taking on a new & challenging role, I know I will persevere in 2023!!!

#happynewyear #perseverance #iwillsurvive #wordoftheyear #theme #icandothis

FLUTTER ALERT… Love is on the air…. Atlanta... who is Getting MARRIED this Valentine's Day? Maybe this is the event for you.

The event will include a mass ceremony followed by a wedding reception (with dinner, dancing, and entertainment) for all newly hitched couples.

February 14, 2023
4-9 PM
Greystone Building @piedmontpark.
